(17,0,"Equally available to propounding party","Objection, the information sought is equally available to propounding party. Cal. Judges Benchbook Civ. Proc. Discovery (August 2019), § 18.35, citing Code Civ.Proc., § 2030.220, subd. (c) and Alpine Mut. Water Co. v Superior Court (1968) 259 CA2d 45, 54.","Objection, the information sought is equally available to propounding party. Cal. Judges Benchbook Civ. Proc. Discovery (August 2019), § 18.35, citing Code Civ.Proc., § 2030.220, subd. (c) and Alpine Mut. Water Co. v Superior Court (1968) 259 CA2d 45, 54.\n\r\n\rUse Notes\n\rAlpine Mut. Water Co. v Superior Court (1968) 259 CA2d 45 is limited to publicly available documents.","3"),
